            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# Dictate Anywhere 2.2.6

- Fixed AI transcript cleanup so processed text no longer outputs em dashes.
- Strengthened transcript cleanup instructions so long dictation is more aggressively split into sentences, paragraphs, and bullet lists.
- Tightened the post-processing wrappers so formatting instructions are applied more consistently across Apple Intelligence, Ollama, and OpenRouter.
]]></description>
